<p>Let's start this document as a how to/best practices for the workroom</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The event/task module automatically adds it to the calendar in whatever workspace you have selected on the sidebar. Unfortunately, all is not an option and it'll just put it in your personal folder (which i learned the hard way). You can choose what workspace when you create an event under workspaces or you can go back and edit it by going to the calendar, clicking the event and then hitting edit.</p>